OL,3,CAlopecia patient: 'I didn't even look
OL,4,Cat myself in the mirror'
OL,6,FA woman who lost her hair in six weeks
OL,7,Fdue to alopecia is calling for greater
OL,8,Fsupport and understanding of the
OL,9,Fcondition.
OL,11,FElena McGowan explains she felt
OL,12,F"completely alone" after being
OL,13,Fdiagnosed and decided to pay for
OL,14,Fprivate care following a comment by
OL,15,Fher doctor.
OL,17,FShe says she was told "it was just
OL,18,Fhair" which made her believe she was
OL,19,Fnot being taken seriously.
