OL,3,CAlopecia patient: 'I didn't even look
OL,4,Cat myself in the mirror'
OL,6,FElena adds the rate of hair loss
OL,7,Fdestroyed her self-confidence so she
OL,8,Fstarted Jersey's first support group
OL,9,Ffor others going through a similar
OL,10,Fexperience to have a safe space to
OL,11,Fshare their feelings.
OL,13,FShe says: "It's important to cry, to
OL,14,Flet it out to someone who gets it.
OL,16,F"It was as if I lost myself, I felt
OL,17,Fawful. I didn't recognise myself in
OL,18,Fthe mirror, I lost my crown and glory,
OL,19,FI lost my shelter.
