OL,3,CAlopecia patient: 'I didn't even look
OL,4,Cat myself in the mirror'
OL,6,FPeople living with the condition in
OL,7,FJersey are calling for more support as
OL,8,Fthere is no specialist on the island.
OL,10,FNicola Smith, whose 8-year-old
OL,11,Fdaughter Emily has alopecia, claims a
OL,12,FGP told her to read about the
OL,13,Fcondition rather than giving any
OL,14,Fempathy, sympathy or support.
OL,16,FShe explained: "When we had the GP
OL,17,Fdiagnosis for Emily, I was told to go
OL,18,Fread a book targeted at teenagers for
OL,19,Fconfidence and resilience and I was
OL,20,Fleft feeling like, 'I don't know where
OL,21,Fto go from here'."
