OL,6,FMedical experts say it is unlikely the
OL,7,Fisland will get a specialist but agree
OL,8,Fmore can be done to support those with
OL,9,Falopecia.
OL,11,FDoctor Ed Klaber says: "It's always
OL,12,Ftricky in Jersey because of the size
OL,13,Fof our population.
OL,15,F"We're not going to be able to justify
OL,16,Fthe employment of a specialist for
OL,17,Fhair loss, but what we can look to do
OL,18,Fis have a specific service or clinic."
