OL,4,Cat myself in the mirror'
OL,6,FHe raised that alopecia is more than a
OL,7,Fphysical condition, adding: "Most
OL,8,Fpeople don't think about the mental
OL,9,Fimpact it has.
OL,11,F"The psychological consequences of
OL,12,Fhair loss can be huge. Anyone who
OL,13,Fknows someone going through this, they
OL,14,Fare probably having the greatest
OL,15,Fpsychological turmoil so be
OL,16,Fconsiderate and that's for those in
OL,17,Fhealthcare or those in the general
OL,18,Fpublic.
